---
title: Hot Chicken Sandwich with Gravy and Creamy Chive Mash
description: This comfort dish is inspired by the Quebecois "Hot Chicken Sandwich". In our version, we drop the "sandwich" and make an open-faced wonder! Rich chicken gravy smothers tender chicken atop toasted buns. We've swapped the usual green peas, to tender green beans.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hot-chicken-e838e5de.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/hot-chicken-sandwich-60d1b93d17e83732b511f0ff-6ff5915e.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/hot-chicken-sandwich-60d1b93d17e83732b511f0ff
